{
  "stem": "2833.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We knew it was in the east because they always said, you know, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it goes to the east.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the name Auschwitzen was Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we knew it was another camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we really didn't know what was going on there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What kind of camp?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Train-- that was a regular train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, plain wooden benches and normal windows, like a third-class, as they called it at that time, train would run, you know.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was still normal train.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we got out there and saw where we were.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I have a, had a dear friend who was a musician-- was a marvelous pianist.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he played also saxophone, and he played the harmonica.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he had to play in the band-- in the famous band in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Whenever a train arrived, the band came, played.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Kurt Mayer.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Kurt Mayer used to be a pianist in Prague before the war in a very lovely nightclub there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I knew him from, you know, from then already.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then, of course, in Terezin, always we saw a lot of him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, you know, he was one of our group of friends.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he-- I saw him at the station.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he managed, when we walked to Mr.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Mengele, and [SIGHS] that is the man who said, left or right, which we didn't know what it means anyway at, at that point.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And [SIGHS] he managed afterwards, when I walked on-- and he managed to get to me and asked me-- he told me he was with  my husband and asked me if I should tell him.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I said, no, because my husband was happy knowing that I'm protected in Terezin.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He didn't know I'm going to join him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He would have been much more unhappy.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
